caseTitle: Waseem Zafar Jutt, Chak No.66/E.B Tehsil Arifwala, Dist.Pakpattan Sharif. v. Mian Muhammaed Amjad Joya & others
tagline: Leave is granted to examine the question whether an appeal can be filed by a candidate against acceptance of the nomination papers of an opposing candidate in terms of section 63 of the Elections Act, 2017.
